CRICKET - SRI LANKA 192 - 6 DEC AND 213 - 1 , LEEWARDS 148 - CLOSE . Sri Lanka , 44 ahead on first innings , were 213 - 1 at the close on the second day of their three - day match against the Leeward Islands on Monday . Scores : Sri Lanka 192 - 6 dec and 213 - 1 ( R . Arnold 104 not out , M . Atapattu 90 not out ) . Leeward Islands 148 ( M . Muralitharan 4 - 34 ) . 
